sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant HTTP as HTTP /graphql
    participant Engine as ExecutionGraphQlService
    participant Ctrl as @Controller
    participant Svc as Service layer

    note over Client,HTTP: Query / Mutation — HTTP POST
    Client->>HTTP: POST /graphql { query }
    HTTP->>Engine: execute(WebGraphQlRequest)
    Engine->>Ctrl: @QueryMapping / @MutationMapping
    Ctrl->>Svc: apply domain event
    Svc-->>Ctrl: updated aggregate
    Engine->>Ctrl: @SchemaMapping (nested fields)
    Ctrl-->>Engine: resolved value
    Engine-->>Client: { data: … }

